    <item>
      <title>Imagery</title>
      <link>https://borhuub.github.io/writeups/imagery/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://borhuub.github.io/writeups/imagery/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;imagery_machine&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; src=&#34;https://borhuub.github.io/img/imagery/imagery_machine.png&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1 id=&#34;reconocimiento&#34;&gt;Reconocimiento&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bash&#34; data-lang=&#34;bash&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;❯ sudo nmap -p- --open -sS --min-rate &lt;span class=&#34;m&#34;&gt;5000&lt;/span&gt; -vvv -n -Pn 10.129.54.76 -oG ports
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;sudo&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;]&lt;/span&gt; contraseña para borhub:
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;Lo siento, pruebe otra vez.
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;sudo&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;]&lt;/span&gt; contraseña para borhub:
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;Host discovery disabled &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;-Pn&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;. All addresses will be marked &lt;span class=&#34;s1&#34;&gt;&amp;#39;up&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt; and scan &lt;span class=&#34;nb&#34;&gt;times&lt;/span&gt; may be slower.
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;Starting Nmap 7.97 &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt; https://nmap.org &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; at 2025-09-30 15:18 +0200
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;Initiating SYN Stealth Scan at 15:18
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;Scanning 10.129.54.76 &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;m&#34;&gt;65535&lt;/span&gt; ports&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;]&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;Discovered open port 22/tcp on 10.129.54.76
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;Discovered open port 8000/tcp on 10.129.54.76
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;Completed SYN Stealth Scan at 15:18, 12.98s elapsed &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;m&#34;&gt;65535&lt;/span&gt; total ports&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;Nmap scan report &lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; 10.129.54.76
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;Host is up, received user-set &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;0.056s latency&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;.
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;Scanned at 2025-09-30 15:18:37 CEST &lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; 13s
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;Not shown: &lt;span class=&#34;m&#34;&gt;62931&lt;/span&gt; closed tcp ports &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;reset&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span class=&#34;m&#34;&gt;2602&lt;/span&gt; filtered tcp ports &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;no-response&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;Some closed ports may be reported as filtered due to --defeat-rst-ratelimit
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;PORT     STATE SERVICE  REASON
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;22/tcp   open  ssh      syn-ack ttl &lt;span class=&#34;m&#34;&gt;63&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;8000/tcp open  http-alt syn-ack ttl &lt;span class=&#34;m&#34;&gt;63&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;Read data files from: /usr/bin/../share/nmap
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;Nmap &lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;done&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span class=&#34;m&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt; IP address &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;m&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt; host up&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; scanned in 13.05 seconds
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;           Raw packets sent: &lt;span class=&#34;m&#34;&gt;68942&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;3.033MB&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;|&lt;/span&gt; Rcvd: &lt;span class=&#34;m&#34;&gt;63149&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;2.526MB&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;❯ ports.py ports
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;🔍 Puertos encontrados:
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;  ➜  &lt;span class=&#34;m&#34;&gt;22&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;  ➜  &lt;span class=&#34;m&#34;&gt;8000&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;¡Puertos copiados en el portapapeles!
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;❯ sudo nmap -sCV -p 22,8000 10.129.54.76 -oN targeted
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;Starting Nmap 7.97 &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt; https://nmap.org &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; at 2025-09-30 15:19 +0200
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;Nmap scan report &lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; 10.129.54.76
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;Host is up &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;0.14s latency&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;.
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;PORT     STATE SERVICE VERSION
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;22/tcp   open  ssh     OpenSSH 9.7p1 Ubuntu 7ubuntu4.3 &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;Ubuntu Linux&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt; protocol 2.0&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;|&lt;/span&gt; ssh-hostkey:
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;|&lt;/span&gt;   &lt;span class=&#34;m&#34;&gt;256&lt;/span&gt; 35:94:fb:70:36:1a:26:3c:a8:3c:5a:5a:e4:fb:8c:18 &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;ECDSA&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;|&lt;/span&gt;_  &lt;span class=&#34;m&#34;&gt;256&lt;/span&gt; c2:52:7c:42:61:ce:97:9d:12:d5:01:1c:ba:68:0f:fa &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;ED25519&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;8000/tcp open  http    Werkzeug httpd 3.1.3 &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;Python 3.12.7&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;|&lt;/span&gt;_http-title: Image Gallery
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;|&lt;/span&gt;_http-server-header: Werkzeug/3.1.3 Python/3.12.7
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;Service Info: OS: Linux&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt; CPE: cpe:/o:linux:linux_kernel
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;Service detection performed. Please report any incorrect results at https://nmap.org/submit/ .
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;Nmap &lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;done&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span class=&#34;m&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt; IP address &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;m&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt; host up&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; scanned in 9.25 seconds
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h1 id=&#34;enumeración-web&#34;&gt;Enumeración web&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Nuestro siguiente paso será enumerar la página web, una vez entramos a la web vemos que tenemos tanto un panel de login y de register. Con lo cual nos registramos en la web para ver funcionalidades descubrimos.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
